{"tid":2437794,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"綾瀨遙風騷晒胸 賀新劇再創佳績","createTime":"2021-03-08T05:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T16:27:43.000Z","uid":16659,"like":149,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"31fe9187e1c1b98427cd84c6bfb1b11be8aeba07","tid":2437794,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nIASzCUg6Dc17Pq10gX-KRs_bRE=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IOFB5SQVANBA5IT7LP6LAVZF3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnIASzCUg6Dc17Pq10gX-KRs_bRE%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIOFB5SQVANBA5IT7LP6LAVZF3M.jpg&h=4598afe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由國民女星綾瀨遙主演的TBS電視台新劇《天國與地獄》，開播以來成績理想，昨晚播出的第八集收視有14.8%，比起上集的14.7%微升0.1%，已連續八星期錄得超過13%以上的收視佳績。<br />\n<br />\n綾瀨遙與《天國與地獄》的名編劇森下佳子先後多次合作，曾炮製出《白夜行》、《仁醫》及《繼母與女兒的藍調》等人氣劇集，今次由綾瀨遙夥拍高橋一生，講述女主角望月彩子是個充滿正義感的女刑警，高橋一生則演連環殺人案疑犯日高陽斗，兩人在月圓之夜竟然靈魂對調，演員表現與故事鋪排均贏盡讚賞，在今季日劇中之成績可謂一枝獨秀。<br />\n<br />\n《天國與地獄》還有兩集便到大結局，劇情交代到望月與日高再次碌落樓梯，未知能否成功還原肉身，下集更會聯手出擊，有望進一步打動收視成績。綾瀨遙在該劇帶挈下氣勢如虹，本月24日是她的36歲生日，日前她被傳媒拍得穿上FBI的衛衣前往做Gym，而綾瀨遙代言的UNIQLO近日再有新廣告推出，她穿白色背心上陣，風騷晒其驕人上圍，夠晒養眼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CkQy8BwhQNb7E3Y_pMSZ0RSSxtk=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GLUHBJMHVVF6NETMEBJUAQDCO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCkQy8BwhQNb7E3Y_pMSZ0RSSxtk%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGLUHBJMHVVF6NETMEBJUAQDCO4.jpg&h=b9d3ab42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OFfeNvKfcrJsRrgJr6nJl65D2x8=/802x468/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LPMOSNZZWNA7VOJ7FNOWAZFWWA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOFfeNvKfcrJsRrgJr6nJl65D2x8%3D%2F802x468%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLPMOSNZZWNA7VOJ7FNOWAZFWWA.jpg&h=778caf1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MsIJ1py7TAKlIB51Pfp5RjG570Y=/802x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K7MADCHAGJG37KDGA2FNPZOY5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMsIJ1py7TAKlIB51Pfp5RjG570Y%3D%2F802x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK7MADCHAGJG37KDGA2FNPZOY5Y.jpg&h=099b2da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SOt_luJToP9ZK-ApePJkip5JbBg=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OEY7CMDKTBAHLECY35A275CNPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSOt_luJToP9ZK-ApePJkip5JbBg%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOEY7CMDKTBAHLECY35A275CNPA.jpg&h=dd94601f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/seFzWUY5h5O2XMXVtmnoDqj0gEA=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WYZXAGYVAZEDTNHDMV7I6LGAQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FseFzWUY5h5O2XMXVtmnoDqj0gEA%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWYZXAGYVAZEDTNHDMV7I6LGAQI.jpg&h=215e3c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2i5Kjfv2cidBFD5FvRblBNOqgq0=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MCFE4H4M5NAN7BHCS4VSHQC6TQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src